032package org.opengis.test;
033
034
035/**
036 * Base class for exceptions thrown when a numerical computation did not produced
037 * the expected value.
038 *
039 * @author  Martin Desruisseaux (Geomatys)
040 * @version 3.1
041 * @since   3.1
042 */
043public abstract class ComputationFailure extends AssertionError {
044    /**
045     * For cross-version compatibility.
046     */
047    private static final long serialVersionUID = 7082843147964652170L;
048
049    /**
050     * Creates a new exception with the given message.
051     *
052     * @param message  the details message.
053     */
054    public ComputationFailure(final String message) {
055        super(message);
056    }
057}
